        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <lev1>
                    <title>Cap Cover and Input Shaft Seal Kit</title>
                    <para>An improved bearing cap cover seal and input shaft seal kit is available for Sheppard M90, and
                        M100 power steering gears. This letter explains the difference between the seal kits and which
                        Sheppard M-Series steering gear they fit.
                    </para>
                    <para>All steering gears with a grease zerk fitting in the bearing cap cover will use part number
                        1685190C92 bearing cap cover kit (
                        <hotlnk xrefid="f9105011">Figure 1</hotlnk>).
                    </para>
                    <specpara>
                        <note>
                            <para>Steering gears with a grease zerk fitting on the bearing cap cover cannot use this
                                kit.
                            </para>
                        </note>
                    </specpara>
                    <figure id="f9105011" figsize="pg-wide">
                        <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g9105011.webp" type="webp" resolution="200"/>
                        <caption>Figure 1. 1685190C92 Bearing Cap Cover Kit On M-Series Steering Gears Without A Grease
                            Zerk Fitting
                        </caption>
                        <calloutgroup>
                            <callout1>1. INPUT SHAFT</callout1>
                            <callout1>2. 7/8 INCH DIA RED SEAL, 1 INCH DIA WHITE SEAL</callout1>
                            <callout1>3. 3/4 INCH DIA ORANGE SEAL</callout1>
                            <callout1>4. CAPSCREW</callout1>
                            <callout1>5. BEARING CAP</callout1>
                            <callout1>6. THRUST WASHER</callout1>
                            <callout1>7. THRUST BEARING</callout1>
                            <callout1>8. GREASE ZERK FITTING</callout1>
                            <callout1>9. SEAL SPACER</callout1>
                        </calloutgroup>
                    </figure>
                    <table id="t9105011" frame="all">
                        <title>Parts Information For Steering Gears Manufactured Without A Grease Zerk Fitting</title>
                        <tgroup cols="3" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
