                    </table>
                    <para>All steering gears with a grease zerk fitting in the bearing cap cover will use seal kit part
                        number 1685676C92 (
                        <hotlnk xrefid="f9105012">Figure 2</hotlnk>).
                    </para>
                    <figure id="f9105012" figsize="pg-wide">
                        <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g9105012.webp" type="webp"/>
                        <caption>Figure 2. 1685676C92 Seal Kit For M-Series Steering Gears With A Grease Zerk Fitting In
                            The Bearing Cap Cover
                        </caption>
                        <calloutgroup>
                            <callout1>1. INPUT SHAFT</callout1>
                            <callout1>2. 7/8 INCH DIA RED SEAL, 1 INCH DIA WHITE SEAL</callout1>
                            <callout1>3. 3/4 INCH DIA ORANGE SEAL</callout1>
                            <callout1>4. CAPSCREW</callout1>
                            <callout1>5. BEARING CAP</callout1>
                            <callout1>6. THRUST WASHER</callout1>
                            <callout1>7. THRUST BEARING</callout1>
                            <callout1>8. GREASE ZERK FITTING</callout1>
                            <callout1>9. INPUT SEAL</callout1>
                            <callout1>10. COVER O-RING</callout1>
                            <callout1>11. SALT SEAL</callout1>
                            <callout1></callout1>
                        </calloutgroup>
                    </figure>
                    <table id="t9105012" frame="all">
